OL,3,CPolice responding to reports of
OL,4,C'active shooter' at Michigan synagogue
OL,6,FPolice are responding to reports of an
OL,7,F"active shooter" at a synagogue in
OL,8,FMichigan.
OL,10,FA driver reportedly crashed a truck
OL,11,Finto the Temple Israel synagogue in
OL,12,FWest Bloomfield Township, a Detroit
OL,13,Fsuburb, before shots were fired.
OL,15,FOakland County Sheriff Mike Bouchard
OL,16,Fconfirmed during an earlier press
OL,17,Fconference that security at the
OL,18,Fsynagogue had engaged in gunfire with
OL,19,Fat least one person, and that no one
OL,20,Fwas in custody.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@PO]
