OL,3,CPolice responding to reports of
OL,4,C'active shooter' at Michigan synagogue
OL,6,FSmoke could be seen billowing from the
OL,7,Fbuilding's roof, while footage from
OL,8,Fthe scene shows dozens of police
OL,9,Fvehicles surrounding the building.
OL,11,FFBI Director Kash Patel said agents
OL,12,Fare on scene of an "apparent vehicle
OL,13,Framming and active shooter situation"
OL,14,Fat the synagogue.
OL,16,FSome parents collected their children
OL,17,Ffrom an early childhood learning
OL,18,Fcenter inside the building after
OL,19,Fgetting approval from police, while
OL,20,FWest Bloomfield School District went
OL,21,Fon lockdown.
