OL,3,CPolice responding to reports of
OL,4,C'active shooter' at Michigan synagogue
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMichigan's governor Gretchen Whitmer
OL,12,Fissued a statement saying she was
OL,13,Ftracking developments.
OL,15,F"This is heartbreaking," she said.
OL,16,F"Michigan's Jewish community should be
OL,17,Fable to live and practice their faith
OL,18,Fin peace."
