OL,3,CPolice responding to reports of
OL,4,C'active shooter' at Michigan synagogue
OL,6,FTemple Israel calls itself the
OL,7,Fnation's largest Reform synagogue,
OL,8,Fwith 12,000 members. according to its
OL,9,Fwebsite.
OL,11,FIt has an early childhood education
OL,12,Fcenter and offers educational programs
OL,13,Ffor families and adults.
OL,15,FThe website says the synagogue is
OL,16,F"passionate about helping Jewish
OL,17,Fcommunities across the globe" and that
OL,18,Fits mission is to "create a community
OL,19,Fbuilding through the lens of Reform
OL,20,FJudaism".
